title: Newly updated 2 bed with sunroom (or 3rd bedroom), house, laundry
app_fee: $30 fee paid directly to online application, includes credit check
posting_body: ['2 bedroom house with bonus sun room (possible 3rd bedroom / office / den), 1.5 bathroom house, laundry and garage!', 'Be the first to live in this remodeled open floor plan living/dining/kitchen.', 'Brand new appliances; gas range, refrigerator, dishwasher', 'Unit includes:', '*Open floor plan, living dining, kitchen', '*Two large bedrooms with adjoining sunroom, that could be a 3rd bedroom or home office', '*Newly renovated kitchen including new appliances: gas range, refrigerator, dishwasher', '*Laundry in-unit (Machines are to be maintained by Tenant)', '*Conveniently located to Muni (N-Judah), Irving shopping and commercial area, UCSF Medical Center.', '*Walk Score: 93 (Walker’s Paradise)', 'Additional Notes:', "*Security Deposit $5,750.00 (does not include last month's rent)", '*Tenant to pay all utilities.', '*Laundry machines are to be tenant-maintained.', '*NO smoking, NO pets.', '*Minimum 1-year lease.', 'Applicants must have good credit, references and meet minimum income requirements.', "Renters' Insurance will be REQUIRED.", 'Contact via email: Include your name, full email address, phone number, the rental address, and a few days/times you can view the unit.', 'If no email access, call listed phone number and leave message with the same info.', 'T. Okamoto & Co.', 'CA Lic. 00319705']
